---
title: Fig Beef Burgers with Grilled Nectarine Salad and Ready-to-Cook Patties
description: You won't be able to resist these prime-rib beef burgers covered in melty cheese, topped with grilled onions and dolloped with sweet fig spread. We're also bringing major summer flare to the side salad with flame-licked nectarines.
